com.is2t.mwt.model
Class ListHolder

java.lang.Object
  ej.microui.Model
      com.is2t.mwt.model.ListHolder

public class ListHolder
extends ej.microui.Model

Holds a list of objects with a selection. Designed to be used as a model for widgets. Notifies its listeners when the selection changes.
